{"title": "Next Things, and Dorrie's Day", "description": "Two short stories about young people who find themselves in difficult circumstances, written in 1880.\r\n\r\n<i>Next Things</i> relates of two brothers, recently orphaned. They cannot live together anymore, so one goes to a wealthy home on the edge of town, and the other goes to work in a grocer's shop. Each takes their mother's advice to find the <i>next thing</i> to do, and do it. \r\n\r\nIn <i>Dorrie's Day</i> we have a grown-up little girl who gets lost on a train, and relates the family's search for her and her own adventures. Both of the stories contain a temperance theme. - Summary by TriciaG", "duration": 8662, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "157", "name": " Pansy"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/nextthings_2411_librivox/nextthings_2411.jpg", "copyright_year": "1880", "genres": ["Religion", "Christian Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Joy M."}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Next Things, Chapter 1", "readers": [3157], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/nextthings_2411_librivox/nextthings_01_pansy_64kb.mp3", "duration": 437}, {"section": 2, "title": "Next Things, Chapter 2", "readers": [3157], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/nextthings_2411_librivox/nextthings_02_pansy_64kb.mp3", "duration": 423}, {"section": 3, "title": "Next Things, Chapter 3", "readers": [3157], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/nextthings_2411_librivox/nextthings_03_pansy_64kb.mp3", "duration": 458}, {"section": 4, "title": "Next Things, Chapter 4", "readers": [3157], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/nextthings_2411_librivox/nextthings_04_pansy_64kb.mp3", "duration": 424}, {"section": 5, "title": "Next Things, Chapter 5", "readers": [3157], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/nextthings_2411_libri